Architecture: all
Description: A Perl6 Implementation - Documentation
 Pugs is an implementation of Perl 6, written in Haskell. It aims to implement
 the full Perl6 specification, as detailed in the Synopses at
 http://dev.perl.org/perl6/synopsis/
 .
 Homepage: http://pugscode.org/
